    "=======================\n",
    "\n",
    "Traditional uncertainty calculation\n",

    "$$ Y_{new} = X_{new}\\beta$$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$ \\delta Y_{new} = t(0.95,n-2)\\Bigg\\{\n",
    "                          \\frac{Y^TY-\\beta^TX^TY}{n-2}\\Bigg[X_{new}(X^TX)^{-1}X_{new}^T+\\frac{1}{n}\\Bigg]\n",
